Subject: [PATCH] feat: support sublime text colors

---
 src/services/jsonDocumentSymbols.ts |   4 +-
 src/utils/colors.ts                 | 121 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++-
 2 files changed, 122 insertions(+), 3 deletions(-)

